snippet.title: Wastelander - Colony Building Game - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Wastelander is a much anticipated indie roguelike colony building game, that will be available on Steam starting on September 5th 2023!

Wishlist or purchase at: https://store.steampowered.com/app/16...
